Harnessing these intense skin-purifying ingredients, this Hydrating Booster leaves skin looking luminous, fresh and radiant day and night. Directions Shake well before applying this serum. Title: Sans [ceuticals] Protein Moisture Infusion 20
Description: Originally developed as a hair treatment for professional use only, this new-generation hydrating and restructuring serum targets the internal structure of the hair fibre. It contains a powerful combination of small molecular proteins, bio-lipids and natural AHAs (critical for pH balancing) to protect, soften and nourish the hair.Features + Benefits+ Ceramide Complex (Glycosphingolipids & Phospholipids) Protects hair against environmental damage and the effects of mechanical and chemical treatments by replenishing lipids within the hair and scalp; improving softness, resilience and shine. It also works to soothe sensitive, itchy and irritated skin and helps treat dandruff prone scalps.+ Wheat Amino Acids (Wheat Amino Acids) Due to its small molecular size, this amino acid complex exhibits powerful moisture binding properties and is able to penetrate the hair cuticle to repair from within. Sans [ceuticals] Moisture & Protein Infusion 20 contains 30 times more of these small molecular proteins than our Hydratants, making it a SUPER strength serum.+ Phyto Keratin (Hydrolysed Soy Protein & Hydrolysed Corn Protein & Hydrolysed Wheat Protein) Small molecular proteins that are able to penetrate the hair cuticle to restructure and fortify from within.To UseApply after using Sans [ceuticals] Wash. Blot excess moisture and spray thoughout mid-lengths and ends.You will need roughly 15-20 pumps. Massage into hair then rinse. Use weekly to maintain optimum health and keep hair ultra glossy and shiny. Finish off with an application of Sans [ceuticals] Hydratant.

Title: Sans [ceuticals] Nourishing Hair Hydratant
Description: Packed full of goodies such as avocadin lipids, phytoceramides and amino acids, Sans [ceuticals] Nourishing Hair Hydratant will quench and protect hair, leaving it smooth and glossy. This deluxe formula contains the latest in colour-safe technology to give your colour extra staying power.Features + Benefits+ Ceramide Complex (Glycosphingolipids & Phospholipids) Protects hair against environmental damage and the effects of mechanical and chemical treatments by replenishing lipids within the hair and scalp; improving softness, elasticity and shine. It also works to soothe sensitive, itchy and irritated skin and helps treat dandruff prone scalps.+ Wheat Amino Acids (Wheat Amino Acids) Due to its small molecular size, this amino acid complex exhibits powerful moisture binding properties and is able to effectively penetrate the hair cuticle to repair from within.+ Sunflower Seed Extract (Helianthus Annuus Seed Extract) Neutralises free radicals, protects from UV radiation and reduces colour fade in natural and coloured hair, makes combing wet hair easy, helps as a thermal barrier and improves moisture retention.+ Mango Butter (Irvingia Gabonensis) Pressed from the kernels of mango fruit. Rich in proteins, fats, and vitamin B, mango butter is an intensly lipid rich ingredient for lipid depleted, dry, wiry hair. Restores silkiness and sheen and promotes cell regeneration within the skin. Mango butter also posesses UV protection.Multi Functional TipLeave in for an extra 15 minutes as a luxury hair treatment for dry and damaged hair.

Title: Majik No Keratin, No Synthetic – 100% Human Hair Building Fiber
Description: Hair loss is a very common problem that number of people suffer from. There are number of products available in the market to prevent this problem. If you are suffering from a drastic hair fall and partial baldness, you could opt for Hair Building Fiber by Majik. Majik is a Swiss based brand which is recognized as one of the most reputed hair-care brands all over the world. From the Manufacturer What It Is Majik Hair Building Fibers, made of 100% Human hair, blend undetectably with existing hair strands to instantly create the appearance of naturally thick and full hair. What It Does Instantly fills in thinning areas Conceals hair loss Makes fine hair look completely thick and full Great as a root touch-up between colorings What Else You Need To Know Majik Hair Fibers resist wind, rain, and perspiration for long lasting results in all conditions. Available in nine shades that can be mixed to match Indian hair color, Hair Fibers work for all hair types and textures. Also great for part lines, covering extension tracks and touching up roots between hair color appointments. Easily washes out with shampoo. How to Apply Dry and style hair as usual. Shake Hair Fibers into thinning areas. If applying Hair Fibers near the hairline, use Majik Hairline Optimizer to achieve a natural looking front hairline. Gently pat hair to disperse Hair Fibers. If desired, lightly comb, brush, or style your hair after applying Hair Fibers. For best results, use Majik Hair Fiber Spray to finish for longer-lasting results.
